source: TEXT_SUBFST009_00034_SEQ_00<tab>Celestine, a world-weary veteran of many adventures, is looking for an inexperienced young soul to make a delivery on her behalf.
target: TEXT_SUBFST009_00034_SEQ_00<tab>Die Abenteurerin Celestine scheint eine Lieferung für den Stubben in Auftrag geben zu wollen.

source: TEXT_SUBFST009_00034_SEQ_01<tab>Celestine, a veteran adventurer who has long since grown weary of menial tasks, sizes you up at a glance and declares you the perfect person to undertake her latest commission. Deliver a bag of basic provisions to Tsubh Khamazom at the Bannock.
target: TEXT_SUBFST009_00034_SEQ_01<tab>Celestine möchte, dass du an ihrer Stelle das Proviantpaket zum Stubben bringst und dort bei Tsubh Khamazom ablieferst.

source: TEXT_SUBFST009_00034_SEQ_02<tab>You deliver a bag of basic provisions to Tsubh Khamazom, an unabashed coward who commends your bravery whilst simultaneously questioning your sanity. Though you are proud to have done your bit to aid the gentler souls of Gridania, you are somewhat surprised by her mention of another, earlier payment. Putting the thought from your mind, you look forward to the day when you, too, can foist such drudgery on green adventurers.
target: TEXT_SUBFST009_00034_SEQ_02<tab>Tsubh Khamazom hält den Wald für un<var 16 /var>be<var 16 /var>rechen<var 16 /var>bar und gefährlich. Deshalb ist sie dankbar, dass du dich getraut hast, den Proviant zum Stubben zu bringen.

source: TEXT_SUBFST009_00034_TODO_00<tab>Deliver the provisions to Tsubh Khamazom.
target: TEXT_SUBFST009_00034_TODO_00<tab>Proviantpaket zu Tsubh Khamazom am Stubben bringen
TEXT_SUBFST009_00034_CELESTINE_000_1<tab>He du, wenn du Zeit hast, darfst du mir helfen.

source: TEXT_SUBFST009_00034_CELESTINE_000_2<tab>You know the Bannock, I trust? Fancy taking a bag of basic provisions over there for me? It's not too heavy, mostly filled with dried meats and other bland rations.
target: TEXT_SUBFST009_00034_CELESTINE_000_2<tab>Hier, das Proviantpaket mit Dörrfleisch und anderen Leckereien muss zum Stubben. Kannst du das erledigen?

source: TEXT_SUBFST009_00034_CELESTINE_000_3<tab>It's a straightforward job that I'd do with a smile and a spring in my step...if I were ten years younger. Alas, my tastes have matured. Evolved. Advanced to a higher <var 1A 02 /var>level<var 1A 01 /var>, you might even say.
target: TEXT_SUBFST009_00034_CELESTINE_000_3<tab>Ich habe zwar den Auftrag angenommen, aber so 'n Kinderkram ist echt unter meiner Würde, verstehst du? Das kann <var 08 E905 (('ne Anfängerin)) (('n Anfänger)) /var> wie du erledigen.

source: TEXT_SUBFST009_00034_CELESTINE_000_4<tab>But it's a perfect little task for someone <var 1A 02 /var>fresh-faced<var 1A 01 /var> like you. Worry not─you'll receive appropriate compensation upon delivery, which you may keep with my blessings.
target: TEXT_SUBFST009_00034_CELESTINE_000_4<tab>Die Belohnung kannst du dafür einsacken, klar? Dann mal los!

source:
TEXT_SUBFST009_00034_TSUBHKHAMAZOM_000_10A delivery, eh?
...You're certain you weren't followed?

TEXT_SUBFST009_00034_TSUBHKHAMAZOM_000_11<tab>Yes, this is what I requested. Strange...I was expecting someone with rather more experience. I usually balk at such <var 1A 02 /var>outrageous<var 1A 01 /var> payments prior to delivery.
target: TEXT_SUBFST009_00034_TSUBHKHAMAZOM_000_11<tab>Ach ja, das muss der Proviant sein, den ich bestellt habe. Das wurde aber auch Zeit. Ich kipp schon fast um vor Kohldampf.

source: TEXT_SUBFST009_00034_TSUBHKHAMAZOM_000_12<tab>Honestly, I'm amazed you made it this far! These woods are teeming with anoles and other nasties, ready to make a quick meal of the unprepared.
target: TEXT_SUBFST009_00034_TSUBHKHAMAZOM_000_12<tab>Von der Stadt bis hierhin ist es zwar nicht sehr weit, aber der Wald birgt unbekannte Gefahren. Es gehört schon Mut dazu, sich in den Schatten der Bäume zu wagen.

source:
TEXT_SUBFST009_00034_TSUBHKHAMAZOM_000_13I commend your bravery and thank you for your trouble. Here, take the remainder of the fee. I should be very happy to employ you ag─
Wait! Did you see that!? It looked like an anole! Quickly, go before you bring it here and get us all killed!
target: TEXT_SUBFST009_00034_TSUBHKHAMAZOM_000_13<tab>Danke für die Proviantlieferung. Engagierte Leute wie dich brauchen wir in Gridania!
